Question: The combined images contain exactly two baby baboons, and each image includes at least one small animal with a bigger animal.

Reference Answer: False

Left image URL: http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-fsUFCHffd30/T3JSmmycQvI/AAAAAAAAH4g/tqPztdNPx34/s640/eye.jpg

Right image URL: http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-JtNcnB4FtFw/Ug4IelpD4yI/AAAAAAAAALc/OHiK5RzOi8Y/s1600/olive+baboons.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many baby baboons are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many baby baboons are in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Does the image include at least one small animal with a bigger animal?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Does the image include at least one small animal with a bigger animal?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == 2 and {ANSWER1} == 2 and {ANSWER2} and {ANSWER3}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER4)
```
